# ─── Local AI (Ollama) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are only used as the *default* values in Settings on first load.
# Once the app is running you can override them from the Settings page —
# they are persisted in localStorage.
#
# Install Ollama: https://ollama.com  — then run `ollama pull llama3.2`
OLLAMA_URL="http://localhost:11434"
OLLAMA_MODEL="llama3.2"
